## 📊 Dataset

This project uses the **Flickr8k dataset** — 8,091 images each paired with 5 human-written captions.

### Download

1. Go to [Kaggle — Flickr8k](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/adityajn105/flickr8k)
2. Download and extract
3. Place files in:

```
data/flickr8k/
├── Images/        ← 8,091 .jpg images
└── captions.txt   ← image-caption pairs
```

### Dataset Stats

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Total images | 8,091 |
| Captions per image | 5 |
| Total captions | 40,455 |
| Vocabulary size | ~3,045 words |
| Image size | 224 × 224 |

