## 🚀 API Usage

### Start the server
```bash
uvicorn api.main:app --reload --port 8000
```

### Interactive Docs
Open your browser at: [http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs](http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs)

### Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| GET | `/` | Health check |
| GET | `/platforms` | List supported platforms |
| POST | `/caption` | Generate caption for image |

### Generate Caption

```bash
curl -X POST "http://127.0.0.1:8000/caption" \
  -F "file=@your_image.jpg" \
  -F "platform=instagram"
```

### Sample Response

```json
{
  "raw_description": "a woman in a white shirt standing in a room",
  "caption": "Confidence is my best outfit ✨ #vibes #lifestyle #mood",
  "platform": "instagram",
  "words": 9,
  "status": "success"
}
```

### Platform Examples

| Platform | Example Caption |
|----------|----------------|
| Instagram | "Confidence is my best outfit ✨ #vibes #lifestyle" |
| LinkedIn | "Showing up every day with purpose and passion. #WorkEthic #Goals" |
| Twitter | "main character energy ✨" |
| Email | "A woman in a white shirt standing in a room, for your reference." |

